3. Network Monitoring   [ BASH ]

--->>>  Install monitoring tools
sudo apt install nethogs iftop nload

---->>>  Real-time monitoring
sudo nethogs          # Per-process bandwidth
sudo iftop            # Interface traffic
nload                 # Simple bandwidth meter


